b612-a0d7-43c3-b0fb-026caf451c49" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">sole-occupancy unit</xref> that is located on an <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1153_0.8.0.xml#_30458e20-ec5e-4423-bb83-da0197428cd7" id="_e70f83f6-c49d-4fe3-8748-d249cfa06efd" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">accessible</xref> floor.</p></callout></clause>